"path":"/3/","date":"2020. 09. 02","timeToRead":2,"description":"css의 flex, grid로 만든 Layout에 적용할때 안되던 삽질을 까먹지 않고자 작성한 글입니다.","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>요약 : Treeview를 가변적인 크기의 특정 영역안에서 사용하고싶다면, 부모영역의 높이, 너비가 %만 존재하면 안된다. 부모노드 중 최소 한곳에서 vw, vh 사용할 것.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>현재 사내에서 사용할 웹 기반 솔루션을 개발하고 있습니다. 개발초기라 본격적인 구현에 앞서 UI 레이아웃을 잡고 그 위에 Vuetify 기반의 컨트롤을 배치하고 있었습니다.\n대략 아래와 같은 디자인으로 구성하려했죠.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1280 1040' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-355117976feb481e4bc55afbf3064b0f'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-355117976feb481e4bc55afbf3064b0f)' width='1280' height='1040' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA0CAYAAAA62j4JAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAFOElEQVRo3u2aaW8TRxjH/X2KWkKc2M7h2/Ht%2bAjhqIraF5UQCVcSKK36sh%2bgX6CHKFQq4UW/RqWqL4iSUCiQO7bX3svrteNj/31mNglJREsIrrDLjvTXzM61z/z2mZn1emyfRr5BNjaNTxJz%2bCzzBT6OzSDnv4KJwNQRTeNs6Aoux77FV9lfMZf8BbdS86QHL5U8EHdCB/s8orndstv7Njw8bA9vN2/WGZ/HbOo%2bbibu4esL87geu4svzz7AnexD2OKBS%2bgLDyCZDuPsxTTCsSDsjtNwuPox6DqDQecZOIfslO7HsNeOc8GbuJN5iKuRH3Aj/tO%2bWOczyfudVcKMb7L%2bd%2b/B7xO/h9moOaCrse95fC3yHdW5i2tUdp00Q3lsoKzsRtyMr0epPPoj73du/GcOxeYZDsDv8WHAPginw4XBAQf8vgBGR9xwj3rg8/rR13eGl/Xb7fC6AxjzxcHajTh9GBp0wzUwiv7TTnx0yo7TpwY6qg8/6Iejf4Q0zO8x2DcE14gHfSmyzxHE%2beDncA8FkZqYgs%2bXQNbtRXzED5fDi0gwwe2MBJMIeCPIpiZxY2qW7PZidMgP73CYPCCaRCqVQDgcRjweQzQSRjqdRiIeRyaTRi6Xg8fjQSgUwhjVyU3kMDk5gdR4EqGxIIKhAILBANzuEThdDriGnB2V0%2bmA1%2bfhGh0dhtfrgT9C8M/7EA6FadpeJtvHMHFpGvF0hqZyCJPxEHxkUzabRjRGA89lkM6M48LFc7h9e5bbHY6MIRKOwlYSZJQkFYpagaxUeFpWVIiyCkFUIMkKNE2DqqpcsixzKVSnQm0qFVOsTrVaRVV7KU07fH0iUZ%2bVisbF7sHvQ/m6UuVpSRVN%2b%2bQy2UP2UT2lYtZh9mqVPdsrZLOCUqm838/qiw3Y1Gobf2w2IFQBZQf4fW0HRQ0o68Bvq3We/38NsqjCJhRKnIwoSvzJSpLE0wqlRYldy7v58v7TP65EUeRi